      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag six-speed manual gearbox offers precise throws, sending power through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers and poly-bushes, maintaining factory-spec geometry for neutral handling. While the finish shows minor road patina, the powertrain and drivetrain remain synchronized for peak performance on both canyon roads and the circuit.",
      "price": 34500.0,
